title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Heavy Division 78XH - fixing simbrief integration
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to fix the Heavy Division 78XH Simbrief integration. I will explain you which things you need to check and what additional steps are required to fix the Simbrief integration which is currently broken in the official release of the 78XH.

If you want to update to the developer version of the Heavy Division 78XH download your own copy from the link below:
https://github.com/Heavy-Division/B78XH/archive/refs/heads/main.zip
